title: Soccer stars and Liberia's new president arrive at Elysee Palace
text:
Soccer stars and Liberia's new president arrive at Elysee Palace 12:03pm EST - 00:45 
French President Emmanuel Macron received Liberia's Weah and soccer players Mbappe and Drogba at the Elysee Palace in Paris. Rough cut
